# REST Client file Inventory

### Create a new trip
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/journeys/inventory/trips
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwiZW1haWwiOiJqb2huLmRvZUBlbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpc0FkbWluIjp0cnVlLCJpYXQiOjE3ODIwODU5OTQsImV4cCI6MTc4MjA5Njc5NH0.X_tcuf46IP6lHfa2C-YvoNJEW9yQDjsfFFeq1Qo2DAms5ArngAV2SqjVh6j26MoE

{
  "departureDate": "2026-06-25T12:00:00",
  "arrivalDate": "2026-06-26T20:00:00-03:00",
  "basePrice": 150.00,
  "busId": 2,
  "driverId": 3,
  "locationOriginId": 2,
  "locationDestinationId": 1
}

### Update trip by ID
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/journeys/inventory/trips
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwiZW1haWwiOiJqb2huLmRvZUBlbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpc0FkbWluIjp0cnVlLCJpYXQiOjE3ODE4ODQ4ODcsImV4cCI6MTc4MTg5NTY4N30.1U0zGRV0dFgcjpAMgbnKCnFp0fIadVGBBki28EcKhCxIWOJEZrkwpLmLPx0rGqXg

{
  "id": 2,
  "departureDate": 300.00
}

### Delete trip by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/journeys/inventory/trips/6
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwiZW1haWwiOiJqb2huLmRvZUBlbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpc0FkbWluIjp0cnVlLCJpYXQiOjE3ODIwNDcyNDQsImV4cCI6MTc4MjA1ODA0NH0.carSle-qcDI1w7JC388uNqgSrPzYhh4VaMS-6gJRbadN9i3P6gPaXQsw6mWb3quJ

